channel.description:
[img]http://img149.imageshack.us/img149/7906/teamorb.png[/img]
Welcome to Orbit Studios
Hello guys this is Orb i have currently decided to make a 317 yet Again ! So i will be needing help as there will be many features made on this new 317 Server - I hope to enjoy working with you guys.
Contact me - alexsumner@live.co.uk
Head Developer - Orb Client Developer - Open Server Developer - Open Graphics - Open
I Hope to make this a great 317 once everything is coded and works this will be hosted.
Aim : Increase the standards of a 317 ! Only have good customs inside. Home In Edgeville
The Team are Currently looking for Developers through out the process such as Coders (Client ) Designers( All Gfx ) Coder ( Server )
You will be well treated and this work is Voluntary so i wont be paying - Working for me Will pay in the future .
